snippet.title: Sonic Galactic: Sonic is fucking balling
snippet.description:
What's Sonic doing with his dropdash now? Dashing up walls? Wall hopping?  Cool little flips? What?? This is impossible, Sonic is absolutely balling. Holy fuck.

This is a repost from our Twitter account! We post more on there, but we figured it was about time to entertain our Youtube channel. Expect more posts here soon, and please enjoy this gameplay compilation!

Credits:

Finished Wall Hop Animation by: https://twitter.com/ThePinkGalaxy55
Song made by RRThiel (based): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HU3j4WCzfiQ
